data.title: 1608) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Sixth or Eighth wife of Ivan the Terrible. she was born in Russia around 1553 she married Ivan in 1581  her son Dmitry of Uglich was born in 1582  Ivan died in 1584 after 3 years of marriage she died sometime between 1608-1612.
